00081 //=== Function =================================================================
00082 
00083 Factory<v8::Function>::return_t
00084 Factory<v8::Function>::New( FunctionCallback callback
00085                           , v8::Local<v8::Value> data) {
00086   v8::Isolate *isolate = v8::Isolate::GetCurrent();
00087   v8::EscapableHandleScope scope(isolate);
00088   v8::Local<v8::ObjectTemplate> tpl = v8::ObjectTemplate::New(isolate);
00089   tpl->SetInternalFieldCount(imp::kFunctionFieldCount);
00090   v8::Local<v8::Object> obj = NewInstance(tpl).ToLocalChecked();
00091 
00092   obj->SetInternalField(
00093       imp::kFunctionIndex
00094     , v8::External::New(isolate, reinterpret_cast<void *>(callback)));
00095 
00096   v8::Local<v8::Value> val = v8::Local<v8::Value>::New(isolate, data);
00097 
00098   if (!val.IsEmpty()) {
00099     obj->SetInternalField(imp::kDataIndex, val);
00100   }
00101 
00102   return scope.Escape(v8::Function::New( isolate
00103                           , imp::FunctionCallbackWrapper
00104                           , obj));
00105 }

00117     tpl->SetInternalFieldCount(imp::kFunctionFieldCount);
00118     v8::Local<v8::Object> obj = NewInstance(tpl).ToLocalChecked();
00119 
00120     obj->SetInternalField(
00121         imp::kFunctionIndex
00122       , v8::External::New(isolate, reinterpret_cast<void *>(callback)));
00123     v8::Local<v8::Value> val = v8::Local<v8::Value>::New(isolate, data);
00124 
00125     if (!val.IsEmpty()) {
00126       obj->SetInternalField(imp::kDataIndex, val);
00127     }
00128 
00129     return scope.Escape(v8::FunctionTemplate::New( isolate
00130                                     , imp::FunctionCallbackWrapper
00131                                     , obj
00132                                     , signature));
